WEBVTT

00:02:29.157 --> 00:02:31.038
(Laughter)

00:02:31.062 --> 00:02:33.259
But when I was feeling
confident and suave,

00:02:33.283 --> 00:02:37.052
I would knock my height down a notch,
just to give the competition a chance.

00:02:37.076 --> 00:02:39.171
(Laughter)

00:02:39.195 --> 00:02:41.298
(Applause)

00:02:41.322 --> 00:02:44.591
Narrow-edged feet allowed me
to climb steep rock fissures,

00:02:44.615 --> 00:02:47.217
where the human foot cannot penetrate,

00:02:47.241 --> 00:02:51.423
and spiked feet enabled me
to climb vertical ice walls,

00:02:51.447 --> 00:02:54.320
without ever experiencing
muscle leg fatigue.

00:02:55.399 --> 00:02:57.589
Through technological innovation,

00:02:57.613 --> 00:03:00.454
I returned to my sport,
stronger and better.